1
00:00:06,860 --> 00:00:08,060
<font color="yellow">(Episode 38)</font>

2
00:00:18,090 --> 00:00:19,490
<font color="yellow">You look beat up.</font>

3
00:00:22,490 --> 00:00:23,560
<font color="yellow">Who was it?</font>

4
00:00:24,460 --> 00:00:27,330
<font color="yellow">Who beat up the Seoul mayor?</font>

5
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:29,490
<font color="yellow">If I tell you,</font>

6
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:33,330
<font color="yellow">are you going to get them back for me?</font>

7
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:34,530
<font color="yellow">Of course.</font>

8
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:37,260
<font color="yellow">How dare they touch my precious meal?</font>

9
00:00:38,530 --> 00:00:39,590
<font color="yellow">Was it Gun Woo?</font>

10
00:00:44,990 --> 00:00:46,160
<font color="yellow">I guess I got it right.</font>

11
00:00:47,690 --> 00:00:49,160
<font color="yellow">You must be really hurt...</font>

12
00:00:49,630 --> 00:00:51,530
<font color="yellow">to get stabbed in the back.</font>

13
00:00:52,390 --> 00:00:54,960
<font color="yellow">I know very well how that feels.</font>

14
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:59,460
<font color="yellow">I've been betrayed by people before, too.</font>

15
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:13,230
<font color="yellow">How did you get stuck in solitary confinement?</font>

16
00:01:15,230 --> 00:01:18,490
<font color="yellow">Seoul Mayor is now in solitary confinement...</font>

17
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,690
<font color="yellow">Your life is so pathetic.</font>

18
00:01:27,290 --> 00:01:32,360
<font color="yellow">It's too early for you to celebrate. Don't make me laugh.</font>

19
00:01:34,630 --> 00:01:36,860
<font color="yellow">Do you know why a food chain exists?</font>

20
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:41,690
<font color="yellow">It's not because the weak committed a crime.</font>

21
00:01:42,390 --> 00:01:45,430
<font color="yellow">That's just how the food pyramid is built.</font>

22
00:01:46,990 --> 00:01:50,830
<font color="yellow">Money and power determine who goes to the top of the pyramid.</font>

23
00:01:52,090 --> 00:01:54,060
<font color="yellow">I've let my place go for a moment,</font>

24
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:57,530
<font color="yellow">but I still have power left in me.</font>

25
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:01,230
<font color="yellow">I'll be out soon, Guk Cheol.</font>

26
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:03,160
<font color="yellow">B World.</font>

27
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,560
<font color="yellow">Your goose that lays golden eggs...</font>

28
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,160
<font color="yellow">will soon be put to death.</font>

29
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:12,860
<font color="yellow">I'm going to eat that goose, and that will be the end of it.</font>

30
00:02:14,390 --> 00:02:16,960
<font color="yellow">Your supporter Hwang Jae Man will abandon you without B World.</font>

31
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:21,790
<font color="yellow">I'm curious to see how you'll get out of jail.</font>

32
00:02:28,330 --> 00:02:29,830
<font color="yellow">Enjoy, Uncle.</font>

33
00:02:31,890 --> 00:02:32,990
<font color="yellow">This is...</font>

34
00:02:34,330 --> 00:02:36,100
<font color="yellow">my last goodwill to you.</font>

35
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:13,590
<font color="yellow">Kang Gi Tan...</font>

36
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:18,290
<font color="yellow">Do Gun Woo!</font>

37
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:06,260
<font color="yellow">Mum, what do you think about this jacket? It's for today's meeting.</font>

38
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:14,430
<font color="yellow">I think it's the new blood pressure medication he started taking.</font>

39
00:04:15,490 --> 00:04:17,520
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with the new medication?</font>

40
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:20,660
<font color="yellow">It doesn't seem to suit him. Also, the stress must have...</font>

41
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:23,330
<font color="yellow">caused a temporary mental derangement.</font>

42
00:04:24,330 --> 00:04:28,050
<font color="yellow">By temporary, do you mean that he'll be back to normal?</font>

43
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:31,190
<font color="yellow">Of course. It's not dementia, so please do not worry.</font>

44
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:34,400
<font color="yellow">Can he still attend the general meeting?</font>

45
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:38,430
<font color="yellow">I think we should wait and see when he wakes up.</font>

46
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,330
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

47
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:44,590
<font color="yellow">Come on, what do you think? Is it too much?</font>

48
00:04:45,690 --> 00:04:47,940
<font color="yellow">Tell your father to come out for his meal.</font>

49
00:04:47,940 --> 00:04:51,050
<font color="yellow">Are you going to make him food?</font>

50
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:53,360
<font color="yellow">I need to check how he's doing.</font>

51
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:58,060
<font color="yellow">Okay. All right.</font>

52
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:06,160
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

53
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:09,230
<font color="yellow">you can attend the general meeting today?</font>

54
00:05:09,230 --> 00:05:10,660
<font color="yellow">I have to go.</font>

55
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,030
<font color="yellow">I won't do you a favour by not going.</font>

56
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:15,060
<font color="yellow">Dr Hwang was right.</font>

57
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:17,860
<font color="yellow">Why does he have to be normal today?</font>

58
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,960
<font color="yellow">You're not very well.</font>

59
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:23,140
<font color="yellow">I think you should rest today.</font>

60
00:05:23,140 --> 00:05:27,460
<font color="yellow">Are you telling me to just sit and watch...</font>

61
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:32,160
<font color="yellow">while the two of you try to steal my money away?</font>

62
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:34,890
<font color="yellow">That's not what I meant. I was just worried about you.</font>

63
00:05:34,890 --> 00:05:37,690
<font color="yellow">When this general meeting is over, you two will get...</font>

64
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:40,590
<font color="yellow">what you deserve!</font>

65
00:05:42,230 --> 00:05:43,760
<font color="yellow">Go ahead.</font>

66
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:47,860
<font color="yellow">No one will care about you even if you come.</font>

67
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:49,960
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong.</font>

68
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:52,460
<font color="yellow">Why isn't Mother eating?</font>

69
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,460
<font color="yellow">Father...</font>

70
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:59,330
<font color="yellow">Go and get her right away.</font>

71
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:00,960
<font color="yellow">I should greet her before I'm off to work.</font>

72
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:03,890
<font color="yellow">Chairman...</font>

73
00:06:03,890 --> 00:06:05,060
<font color="yellow">Your mother...</font>

74
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:08,470
<font color="yellow">didn't want to eat because there's no meat today.</font>

75
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:11,560
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you make any meat dishes?</font>

76
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:14,860
<font color="yellow">This is the reason why I'm always being scolded!</font>

77
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,790
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Honey.</font>

78
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:20,760
<font color="yellow">We ran out of meat today.</font>

79
00:06:21,230 --> 00:06:24,060
<font color="yellow">Go and buy some meat right now.</font>

80
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:26,860
<font color="yellow">If you don't, I won't let you...</font>

81
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:29,490
<font color="yellow">step inside my house!</font>

82
00:06:32,230 --> 00:06:33,430
<font color="yellow">Did you see that?</font>

83
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:36,160
<font color="yellow">This is how your father treated me all these years.</font>

84
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:41,830
<font color="yellow">He treated me like a maid and a slave.</font>

85
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:43,830
<font color="yellow">He was arrogant and commanding.</font>

86
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:49,160
<font color="yellow">We won't have to worry about today's general meeting.</font>

87
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,290
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

88
00:06:51,290 --> 00:06:52,430
<font color="yellow">Okay, Mum.</font>

89
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:05,990
<font color="yellow">She's gone. You should finish your meal.</font>

90
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:09,060
<font color="yellow">That witch.</font>

91
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:13,460
<font color="yellow">How can she treat my mother like that?</font>

92
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:16,530
<font color="yellow">- I told you, she's gone.
-  This is a problem.</font>

93
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:20,140
<font color="yellow">I'm going to take Mother out for a meal.</font>

94
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:21,740
<font color="yellow">Go and get prepared.</font>

95
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:26,360
<font color="yellow">Sir, your mother passed away.</font>

96
00:07:27,330 --> 00:07:29,260
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

97
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:32,530
<font color="yellow">I just said goodnight to her last night!</font>

98
00:07:32,530 --> 00:07:35,460
<font color="yellow">Weren't you putting up an act?</font>

99
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:38,830
<font color="yellow">Your mother died 20 years ago.</font>

100
00:07:40,590 --> 00:07:42,420
<font color="yellow">What do you mean my mother died?</font>

101
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:43,530
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

102
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:45,890
<font color="yellow">She suffered so much.</font>

103
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:50,150
<font color="yellow">I was going to treat her well now. What do you mean she died?</font>

104
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:54,160
<font color="yellow">No, Sir. I'll go and get her right away.</font>

105
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,160
<font color="yellow">Good.</font>

106
00:07:57,890 --> 00:07:59,090
<font color="yellow">I knew it.</font>

107
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,190
<font color="yellow">You were...</font>

108
00:08:02,330 --> 00:08:03,690
<font color="yellow">just joking, right?</font>

109
00:08:03,690 --> 00:08:05,630
<font color="yellow">Yes. I'm sorry, Sir.</font>

110
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:07,060
<font color="yellow">Hurry.</font>

111
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:10,660
<font color="yellow">Go and get Mother. Go on.</font>

112
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:25,260
<font color="yellow">It's me, Gun Woo.</font>

113
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:29,160
<font color="yellow">The chairman has really gone strange.</font>

114
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:33,160
<font color="yellow">I don't think it's temporary.</font>

115
00:08:38,730 --> 00:08:41,360
<font color="yellow">Are you sure it's not dementia?</font>

116
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:44,860
<font color="yellow">Why would I lie to you?</font>

117
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,660
<font color="yellow">Then what is this shot for?</font>

118
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:49,830
<font color="yellow">It's a kind of sedative to reduce your anxiety.</font>

119
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:53,500
<font color="yellow">You can attend the general meeting since you got the shot.</font>

120
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:57,160
<font color="yellow">I knew it. It's impossible...</font>

121
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:59,670
<font color="yellow">to get dementia at this age.</font>

122
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:01,690
<font color="yellow">Please rest up.</font>

123
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:09,500
<font color="yellow">The general meeting is at 4pm today, so rest up until then.</font>

124
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,590
<font color="yellow">Who else has seen the video...</font>

125
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,160
<font color="yellow">of her switching pills?</font>

126
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:16,690
<font color="yellow">Just the shareholders on our side.</font>

127
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,660
<font color="yellow">I guess it won't be leaked then.</font>

128
00:09:21,330 --> 00:09:22,590
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

129
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:25,360
<font color="yellow">What's your plan?</font>

130
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,690
<font color="yellow">You know that your father won't be at the general meeting, right?</font>

131
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:43,630
<font color="yellow">Didn't Mr Gong call you?</font>

132
00:09:44,530 --> 00:09:47,890
<font color="yellow">He's on and off. It's impossible for him to leave home.</font>

133
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:51,260
<font color="yellow">How can we let him be the chairman in that condition?</font>

134
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:54,090
<font color="yellow">I don't need him there, so don't worry.</font>

135
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:58,630
<font color="yellow">You're still so proud, aren't you? You're just like your father.</font>

136
00:09:58,630 --> 00:09:59,760
<font color="yellow">How disgusting.</font>

137
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:03,600
<font color="yellow">- Did you find yourself a house yet?
-  What house?</font>

138
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:06,930
<font color="yellow">Father told me that he told you to move out.</font>

139
00:10:06,930 --> 00:10:08,290
<font color="yellow">I guess you didn't start looking yet.</font>

140
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:12,260
<font color="yellow">How did he even remember to tell you that?</font>

141
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:17,530
<font color="yellow">Your mum's life came to an end because she trusted him too much.</font>

142
00:10:17,530 --> 00:10:20,360
<font color="yellow">You should find another way to live, too.</font>

143
00:10:20,930 --> 00:10:22,730
<font color="yellow">You're so pathetic and poor.</font>

144
00:10:30,130 --> 00:10:31,130
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

145
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:37,930
<font color="yellow">I guess today is...</font>

146
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:40,090
<font color="yellow">the last day I'll see you.</font>

147
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,030
<font color="yellow">Right now,</font>

148
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:49,590
<font color="yellow">we have 4 hours and 47 minutes until the general meeting.</font>

149
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,660
<font color="yellow">Do you want to resign beforehand?</font>

150
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:56,060
<font color="yellow">If so, I'll give you a lot of severance pay...</font>

151
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:59,460
<font color="yellow">so that you can live the rest of your life doing nothing.</font>

152
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,560
<font color="yellow">It's detestable...</font>

153
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:05,030
<font color="yellow">to see a broken family like us.</font>

154
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:07,160
<font color="yellow">You can find a way to live,</font>

155
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,960
<font color="yellow">the company will be saved...</font>

156
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:12,660
<font color="yellow">and our home will regain peace.</font>

157
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:14,230
<font color="yellow">How does that sound?</font>

158
00:11:14,590 --> 00:11:15,590
<font color="yellow">Do you want to resign?</font>

159
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:21,830
<font color="yellow">We have 4 hours and 46 minutes left.</font>

160
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:24,860
<font color="yellow">If you give up before that,</font>

161
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:27,360
<font color="yellow">I'll let you keep your position as a CEO.</font>

162
00:11:28,230 --> 00:11:30,830
<font color="yellow">Do you have earplugs stuffed in your ears?</font>

163
00:11:30,830 --> 00:11:32,930
<font color="yellow">You seriously have trouble understanding.</font>

164
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,560
<font color="yellow">You idiot.</font>

165
00:11:57,830 --> 00:12:00,460
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo may have played that well, but I know he is...</font>

166
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:02,130
<font color="yellow">probably frustrated.</font>

167
00:12:03,130 --> 00:12:05,230
<font color="yellow">You know what?</font>

168
00:12:06,830 --> 00:12:07,980
<font color="yellow">Maybe I should have...</font>

169
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:10,260
<font color="yellow">become the chairman...</font>

170
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:12,190
<font color="yellow">instead of backing Mum.</font>

171
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,360
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo...</font>

172
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,860
<font color="yellow">sent me a video.</font>

173
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,360
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

174
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:34,900
<font color="yellow">- Are these supplements?
-  Yes, Ma'am.</font>

175
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:35,960
<font color="yellow">Take watch.</font>

176
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:52,340
<font color="yellow">Hey, why did you send me this video?</font>

177
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:53,730
<font color="yellow">Take a look.</font>

178
00:12:53,730 --> 00:12:54,920
<font color="yellow">That's her...</font>

179
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:58,100
<font color="yellow">switching Father's blood pressure medicines with vitamins.</font>

180
00:12:58,100 --> 00:13:00,990
<font color="yellow">What in the world are you talking about?</font>

181
00:13:02,060 --> 00:13:04,550
<font color="yellow">You should ask Mr Han to clarify...</font>

182
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:06,590
<font color="yellow">what in the world you just heard.</font>

183
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:12,760
<font color="yellow">Did Mum switch Dad's blood pressure medicine?</font>

184
00:13:14,390 --> 00:13:15,390
<font color="yellow">It's true.</font>

185
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:33,090
<font color="yellow">That little...</font>

186
00:13:35,230 --> 00:13:37,830
<font color="yellow">Hey, get him.</font>

187
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:43,490
<font color="yellow">My gosh, I'll get you.</font>

188
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:50,210
<font color="yellow">My goodness. This is frustrating!</font>

189
00:13:50,210 --> 00:13:51,230
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

190
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:54,190
<font color="yellow">What will you do with that video?</font>

191
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,440
<font color="yellow">What do you think?</font>

192
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,490
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

193
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,960
<font color="yellow">Don't do anything rash.</font>

194
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:02,930
<font color="yellow">I'll send our dear Ms Hwang Gwi Ja to prison.</font>

195
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:07,490
<font color="yellow">She tried to kill my father. Did you think I'd let her go?</font>

196
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:10,590
<font color="yellow">Hey, stop joking.</font>

197
00:14:11,130 --> 00:14:12,860
<font color="yellow">If you were going to send her to prison,</font>

198
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,930
<font color="yellow">you wouldn't have shown me that video.</font>

199
00:14:16,130 --> 00:14:17,840
<font color="yellow">It's something that happened within our family.</font>

200
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,260
<font color="yellow">Let's make this look good.</font>

201
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:21,060
<font color="yellow">- Mr Kim.
-  Yes, Sir.</font>

202
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:32,160
<font color="yellow">(Commission of General Meeting Attendance)</font>

203
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,830
<font color="yellow">That's a document saying that you're giving your shares to me.</font>

204
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:39,830
<font color="yellow">Sign that paper.</font>

205
00:14:42,730 --> 00:14:44,490
<font color="yellow">There aren't heaters in prison.</font>

206
00:14:44,830 --> 00:14:47,590
<font color="yellow">I thought our dear Ms Hwang Gwi Ja can't take the cold.</font>

207
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,930
<font color="yellow">Once this video goes public,</font>

208
00:14:54,930 --> 00:14:56,640
<font color="yellow">your life will be over, too.</font>

209
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,060
<font color="yellow">I'm making this offer...</font>

210
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,560
<font color="yellow">Go ahead.</font>

211
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:09,730
<font color="yellow">Tell everyone about this.</font>

212
00:15:10,060 --> 00:15:13,160
<font color="yellow">Are you keeping your shares over your mum?</font>

