226
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:09,560
<font color="yellow">You'll ruin the company.</font>

227
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,910
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

228
00:16:10,910 --> 00:16:13,930
<font color="yellow">Not only the company, but you'll be in danger, too.</font>

229
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:17,960
<font color="yellow">I'll take care of this.</font>

230
00:16:18,290 --> 00:16:19,830
<font color="yellow">You can back out now.</font>

231
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:25,120
<font color="yellow">Please gather as much asset as you can.</font>

