235
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,390
<font color="yellow">I need at least one more share than them.</font>

236
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:38,660
<font color="yellow">We have only two more hours left.</font>

237
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:43,460
<font color="yellow">Get everyone on SPD...</font>

238
00:16:43,860 --> 00:16:46,380
