00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:27,930
<font color="yellow">Father wouldn't want the company to go down.</font>

246
00:17:27,930 --> 00:17:29,640
<font color="yellow">I have something to tell you.</font>

247
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:30,900
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

248
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:34,230
