00:19:01,390 --> 00:19:03,200
<font color="yellow">Mum! Mum!</font>

279
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,460
<font color="yellow">Mum, this is bad.</font>

280
00:19:05,460 --> 00:19:08,490
