00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:20,560
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

287
00:19:26,460 --> 00:19:29,450
<font color="yellow">Ms Hwang believes me.</font>

288
00:19:29,450 --> 00:19:31,460
<font color="yellow">Thank you for lying.</font>

289
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:34,860
<font color="yellow">She just asked me to come to the general meeting.</font>

290
00:19:34,860 --> 00:19:36,110
<font color="yellow">That sounds good.</font>

291
00:19:36,110 --> 00:19:38,010
<font color="yellow">I was going to take you, Anyways.</font>

292
00:19:38,010 --> 00:19:40,060
<font color="yellow">It's almost time. You must go.</font>

293
00:19:56,390 --> 00:19:57,930
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Pharmaceutical)</font>

