00:20:04,860 --> 00:20:05,860
<font color="yellow">Chairman!</font>

295
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:10,160
<font color="yellow">Dodo Pharmaceutical's shares are suddenly sky-rocketing.</font>

296
00:20:10,490 --> 00:20:12,210
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo must be buying them out.</font>

297
00:20:12,210 --> 00:20:15,230
<font color="yellow">It seems like they took the bait.</font>

298
00:20:15,230 --> 00:20:18,160
<font color="yellow">Now, all we have to do is bomb that ship and make it sink.</font>

