00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:47,680
<font color="yellow">Do you think that was my doing?</font>

306
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:51,030
<font color="yellow">There aren't very many...</font>

307
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:53,060
<font color="yellow">that dare to touch Il Jae.</font>

308
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:56,390
<font color="yellow">I'm curious to know who those few are.</font>

309
00:20:57,160 --> 00:21:00,490
<font color="yellow">Are you saying that it wasn't you?</font>

