00:21:03,460 --> 00:21:04,860
<font color="yellow">that wouldn't be revenge.</font>

312
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:07,460
<font color="yellow">My revenge...</font>

313
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:10,560
<font color="yellow">will be more beautiful...</font>

314
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,700
<font color="yellow">and classy.</font>

