00:21:19,630 --> 00:21:22,460
<font color="yellow">You have a great set of lawyers lined up.</font>

318
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:25,890
<font color="yellow">I admit, I was amazed.</font>

319
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:31,230
<font color="yellow">If he gets probation or acquittal, your name will be added...</font>

