00:21:57,730 --> 00:22:00,360
<font color="yellow">I ate dog food when I was a homeless.</font>

330
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:02,560
<font color="yellow">I will never forget its taste.</font>

331
00:22:03,460 --> 00:22:05,360
<font color="yellow">That's why I plan on letting Il Jae try some.</font>

332
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:08,560
<font color="yellow">Do you understand what I'm talking about?</font>

333
00:22:09,060 --> 00:22:10,230
<font color="yellow">I'll turn...</font>

