00:22:10,930 --> 00:22:12,590
<font color="yellow">Il Jae into a homeless.</font>

335
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:16,360
<font color="yellow">He'll be poor and useless.</font>

336
00:22:17,890 --> 00:22:19,130
<font color="yellow">Just abandon him then.</font>

337
00:22:21,060 --> 00:22:23,630
<font color="yellow">That's the only chance you can avoid...</font>

338
00:22:24,430 --> 00:22:26,360
<font color="yellow">a fight with me.</font>

339
00:22:39,060 --> 00:22:41,030
<font color="yellow">(The 32nd Dodo Group's General Meeting)</font>

340
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:44,060
<font color="yellow">Why is my seat here instead of over there?</font>

341
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:47,260
<font color="yellow">You sold all of your Dodo Pharmaceutical shares.</font>

342
00:22:47,690 --> 00:22:48,960
<font color="yellow">What about my uncle?</font>

343
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:51,930
<font color="yellow">Byun Il Jae must have delegated the rights.</font>

344
00:22:51,930 --> 00:22:55,130
<font color="yellow">It hurts my pride to sit here. I can't stand it.</font>

345
00:22:58,360 --> 00:22:59,760
<font color="yellow">Come sit at the front with me.</font>

