00:23:04,730 --> 00:23:07,690
<font color="yellow">You signed the Shareholders' Voting Agreement. Get up.</font>

348
00:23:08,060 --> 00:23:09,490
<font color="yellow">Don't embarrass me.</font>

349
00:23:09,490 --> 00:23:10,960
<font color="yellow">Get up.</font>

350
00:23:11,330 --> 00:23:12,890
<font color="yellow">Let go of me.</font>

