359
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:52,530
<font color="yellow">I'll invite Chairwoman Hwang to the podium.</font>

360
00:24:00,730 --> 00:24:03,490
<font color="yellow">Now, we'll start the 32nd...</font>

361
00:24:03,490 --> 00:24:06,360
