368
00:24:32,390 --> 00:24:35,390
<font color="yellow">This is urgent. You need to contact him as soon as possible.</font>

369
00:24:35,390 --> 00:24:36,530
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

370
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:43,950
