422
00:28:42,620 --> 00:28:44,790
<font color="yellow">Same goes for Samjoong Group and Taeyang Group.</font>

423
00:28:45,260 --> 00:28:48,390
<font color="yellow">It was thanks to me we managed to stay afloat. If someone else...</font>

424
00:28:48,390 --> 00:28:49,390
<font color="yellow">Chairwoman Hwang!</font>

