<font color="yellow">Don't. My neighbours will report you right away.</font>

643
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:20,100
<font color="yellow">I tried so hard to hold it back.</font>

644
00:41:22,430 --> 00:41:24,230
<font color="yellow">But I just can't tonight.</font>

645
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:39,630
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon, you're the only woman who makes...</font>

646
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:41,260
<font color="yellow">my heart beat faster.</font>

647
00:41:44,390 --> 00:41:46,030
<font color="yellow">The only one in the world.</font>

648
00:41:47,430 --> 00:41:48,730
<font color="yellow">That's you.</font>

649
00:41:50,830 --> 00:41:52,030
<font color="yellow">Marry me.</font>

650
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:55,530
<font color="yellow">- Gun Woo.
