651
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,760
<font color="yellow">I'll wait.</font>

652
00:42:01,830 --> 00:42:03,260
<font color="yellow">Whether it be 10 years or 100.</font>

653
00:42:03,860 --> 00:42:05,330
<font color="yellow">Until you say yes.</font>

654
00:42:51,600 --> 00:42:54,690
<font color="yellow">What made you want to drink at a place like this?</font>

655
00:42:54,690 --> 00:42:56,100
<font color="yellow">If I lived an average life,</font>

656
00:42:56,690 --> 00:42:59,460
<font color="yellow">would I be happy like everyone else?</font>

657
00:43:01,130 --> 00:43:02,930
<font color="yellow">Ever since I was young,</font>

658
00:43:04,230 --> 00:43:06,190
<font color="yellow">I never lacked anything...</font>

659
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:08,830
<font color="yellow">but I was never happy.</font>

660
00:43:10,490 --> 00:43:12,530
<font color="yellow">Mum and Dad always fought,</font>

661
00:43:12,860 --> 00:43:14,430
<font color="yellow">and Gwang Woo only cared about himself.</font>

662
00:43:16,390 --> 00:43:19,830
<font color="yellow">That's how I ended up caring about what was mine.</font>

663
00:43:30,130 --> 00:43:31,490
<font color="yellow">I'm not used to this.</font>

664
00:43:33,100 --> 00:43:34,230
<font color="yellow">You're like a different person.</font>

665
00:43:43,830 --> 00:43:46,030
<font color="yellow">Should I just get married?</font>

666
00:43:46,030 --> 00:43:48,630
<font color="yellow">That's fine for you, but not your husband.</font>

667
00:43:49,160 --> 00:43:50,860
<font color="yellow">I'll marry you.</font>

668
00:43:52,060 --> 00:43:53,130
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

669
00:43:55,660 --> 00:43:57,630
<font color="yellow">Do you dislike me that much?</font>

670
00:44:00,430 --> 00:44:01,690
<font color="yellow">Tell me.</font>

671
00:44:02,490 --> 00:44:05,630
<font color="yellow">Am I not even worth considering?</font>

672
00:44:06,530 --> 00:44:08,730
<font color="yellow">I'm not capable of loving someone.</font>

673
00:44:09,190 --> 00:44:10,390
<font color="yellow">Why not?</font>

674
00:44:10,390 --> 00:44:12,330
<font color="yellow">My scars run too deep.</font>

675
00:44:14,030 --> 00:44:16,060
<font color="yellow">So I can't make anyone happy.</font>

676
00:44:19,260 --> 00:44:21,630
<font color="yellow">You don't have to force yourself.</font>

677
00:44:22,460 --> 00:44:24,260
<font color="yellow">I'll make myself happy.</font>

678
00:44:30,060 --> 00:44:31,930
<font color="yellow">Let's drink.</font>

679
00:44:33,390 --> 00:44:34,760
<font color="yellow">What has gotten into you?</font>

680
00:44:35,260 --> 00:44:37,620
<font color="yellow">You used to hate it when I got drunk.</font>

681
00:44:37,620 --> 00:44:41,260
<font color="yellow">Today, I think you deserve a drink.</font>

682
00:44:41,730 --> 00:44:43,330
<font color="yellow">Do you trust me now?</font>

683
00:44:47,490 --> 00:44:48,630
<font color="yellow">Cheers.</font>

684
00:44:54,360 --> 00:44:55,490
<font color="yellow">Cheers.</font>

685
00:44:57,760 --> 00:45:02,930
<font color="yellow">I love you to death.</font>

686
00:45:02,930 --> 00:45:04,860
<font color="yellow">Why can't you.</font>

687
00:45:04,860 --> 00:45:07,090
<font color="yellow">Stop screaming in my ear!</font>

688
00:45:07,590 --> 00:45:11,870
<font color="yellow">What? Are you saying you can't stand my singing?</font>

689
00:45:11,870 --> 00:45:14,090
<font color="yellow">You dog bone of a jerk.</font>

690
00:45:15,430 --> 00:45:17,590
<font color="yellow">Leave my ear alone!</font>

691
00:45:24,330 --> 00:45:26,130
<font color="yellow">(Do Choong Returns to Dodo)</font>

692
00:45:42,660 --> 00:45:44,660
<font color="yellow">You can't...</font>

693
00:45:45,590 --> 00:45:46,830
<font color="yellow">do this to me.</font>

694
00:45:46,830 --> 00:45:49,390
<font color="yellow">You took from others all your life.</font>

695
00:45:49,930 --> 00:45:51,460
<font color="yellow">How does it feel to lose something?</font>

696
00:46:13,590 --> 00:46:14,730
<font color="yellow">B World.</font>

697
00:46:15,860 --> 00:46:17,930
<font color="yellow">Your goose that lays golden eggs...</font>

698
00:46:18,930 --> 00:46:20,260
<font color="yellow">will die soon.</font>

699
00:46:20,730 --> 00:46:23,560
<font color="yellow">I'm going to eat it so it can't lay any more.</font>

700
00:46:25,660 --> 00:46:27,630
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan, Gun Woo.</font>

701
00:46:28,660 --> 00:46:29,930
<font color="yellow">You two.</font>

702
00:46:31,190 --> 00:46:32,490
<font color="yellow">I will make you...</font>

703
00:46:33,030 --> 00:46:36,330
<font color="yellow">fight each other until you die.</font>

704
00:46:41,330 --> 00:46:43,460
<font color="yellow">4984. You have a visitor.</font>

705
00:46:50,960 --> 00:46:54,260
<font color="yellow">We have to take Dodo Group back.</font>

706
00:46:54,260 --> 00:46:55,960
<font color="yellow">Give up.</font>

707
00:46:57,130 --> 00:46:59,230
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo was tough to beat,</font>

708
00:46:59,590 --> 00:47:02,690
<font color="yellow">but now that Choong is back, it won't be easy.</font>

709
00:47:03,090 --> 00:47:06,730
<font color="yellow">Soon, Gun Woo will take over B World.</font>

710
00:47:06,730 --> 00:47:08,090
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

711
00:47:08,930 --> 00:47:13,960
<font color="yellow">He stabbed me in the back.</font>

712
00:47:16,760 --> 00:47:20,530
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan said he'd make you a beggar.</font>

713
00:47:23,030 --> 00:47:27,260
<font color="yellow">That means he plans to attack B World.</font>

714
00:47:27,660 --> 00:47:31,160
<font color="yellow">That is why I wanted to see you.</font>

715
00:47:33,160 --> 00:47:35,260
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo will purchase B World...</font>

716
00:47:35,260 --> 00:47:38,230
<font color="yellow">for much cheaper than the market price.</font>

717
00:47:38,760 --> 00:47:42,490
<font color="yellow">In exchange for that, ask for the golf course...</font>

718
00:47:42,490 --> 00:47:45,190
<font color="yellow">and home shopping channel Ms Hwang promised.</font>

719
00:47:46,260 --> 00:47:47,590
<font color="yellow">There's no way...</font>

720
00:47:48,360 --> 00:47:51,490
<font color="yellow">he'd accept that offer.</font>

721
00:47:51,930 --> 00:47:54,460
<font color="yellow">In my safe, I have files and evidence...</font>

722
00:47:54,460 --> 00:47:56,950
<font color="yellow">of the corruption Gun Woo committed...</font>

723
00:47:56,950 --> 00:47:59,160
<font color="yellow">while he was in management.</font>

724
00:47:59,160 --> 00:48:01,160
<font color="yellow">You can use that.</font>

725
00:48:01,560 --> 00:48:06,030
<font color="yellow">I knew it. I knew you wouldn't give in so easily.</font>

726
00:48:07,060 --> 00:48:10,560
<font color="yellow">I'll sell the home shopping channel and golf course for a premium...</font>

727
00:48:11,560 --> 00:48:14,190
<font color="yellow">and invest it in Hong Kong's Z Capital.</font>

728
00:48:15,160 --> 00:48:17,000
<font color="yellow">Z Capital?</font>

729
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:21,630
<font color="yellow">It's a private equity fund. They're corporate hunters.</font>

730
00:48:22,090 --> 00:48:26,260
<font color="yellow">The money you siphoned away from the paper company.</font>

731
00:48:26,260 --> 00:48:28,160
<font color="yellow">Is that where it went?</font>

732
00:48:29,030 --> 00:48:30,130
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

733
00:48:31,090 --> 00:48:33,970
<font color="yellow">If we put in that much more money,</font>

734
00:48:33,970 --> 00:48:37,190
<font color="yellow">then we will have a lot of influence...</font>

735
00:48:37,190 --> 00:48:38,530
<font color="yellow">in where Z Capital invests.</font>

736
00:48:39,930 --> 00:48:43,730
<font color="yellow">While Gi Tan and Gun Woo are fighting over Dodo Group,</font>

737
00:48:44,190 --> 00:48:46,160
<font color="yellow">you will get between them?</font>

738
00:48:47,090 --> 00:48:48,360
<font color="yellow">That's my plan.</font>

739
00:48:50,260 --> 00:48:55,160
<font color="yellow">I will see to it that they both go down in flames.</font>

740
00:48:57,390 --> 00:48:58,460
<font color="yellow">Il Jae.</font>

741
00:48:59,860 --> 00:49:04,660
<font color="yellow">I won't be able to help you much longer.</font>

742
00:49:06,090 --> 00:49:11,160
<font color="yellow">I would like you to do me a favour as well.</font>

743
00:49:11,760 --> 00:49:14,930
<font color="yellow">I will do anything you ask.</font>

744
00:49:15,730 --> 00:49:18,990
<font color="yellow">I will tell you what that is...</font>

745
00:49:20,360 --> 00:49:22,230
<font color="yellow">when you get out of here.</font>

746
00:49:34,360 --> 00:49:36,660
<font color="yellow">What will you ask him to do?</font>

747
00:49:38,030 --> 00:49:39,960
<font color="yellow">Of course, he will fund your campaign.</font>

748
00:49:40,430 --> 00:49:44,390
<font color="yellow">I need him to divorce Ji Soo.</font>

749
00:49:45,830 --> 00:49:47,160
<font color="yellow">Il Jae is branded...</font>

750
00:49:47,960 --> 00:49:49,990
<font color="yellow">with a scarlet letter.</font>

751
00:49:51,390 --> 00:49:53,130
<font color="yellow">If I'm to run for president,</font>

752
00:49:53,730 --> 00:49:57,810
<font color="yellow">I need him not to be my son-in-law any more.</font>

753
00:49:57,810 --> 00:50:00,650
<font color="yellow">Will your daughter sign the divorce papers?</font>

754
00:50:00,650 --> 00:50:03,730
<font color="yellow">I will make her sign them, even if it means...</font>

755
00:50:05,130 --> 00:50:06,590
<font color="yellow">threatening to cut ties with her.</font>

756
00:50:14,430 --> 00:50:15,570
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

757
00:50:15,570 --> 00:50:17,660
<font color="yellow">The Chinese shipowners arrived at Dodo Hotel.</font>

758
00:50:18,690 --> 00:50:21,590
<font color="yellow">They're in a meeting with Gi Tan.</font>

759
00:50:26,360 --> 00:50:31,260
<font color="yellow">(We'll pay the price once the ship is completed.)</font>

760
00:50:31,260 --> 00:50:33,990
<font color="yellow">(That is the current trend.)</font>

761
00:50:42,930 --> 00:50:45,030
<font color="yellow">You speak fluent Mandarin.</font>

762
00:50:46,090 --> 00:50:47,160
<font color="yellow">You did well today.</font>

763
00:50:48,430 --> 00:50:49,430
<font color="yellow">Did I really?</font>

764
00:50:49,790 --> 00:50:52,840
<font color="yellow">They seem to like their accommodation.</font>

765
00:50:52,840 --> 00:50:54,030
<font color="yellow">They'd better.</font>

766
00:50:54,030 --> 00:50:56,230
<font color="yellow">I put so much work into their rooms.</font>

767
00:50:59,930 --> 00:51:02,670
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't I meet with the shipowners?</font>

768
00:51:02,670 --> 00:51:03,960
<font color="yellow">You can talk to me.</font>

769
00:51:09,790 --> 00:51:10,830
<font color="yellow">Heavy tail payment?</font>

770
00:51:11,260 --> 00:51:13,130
<font color="yellow">It's a 600,000-dollar deal.</font>

771
00:51:13,130 --> 00:51:14,790
<font color="yellow">Do they want to pay it later?</font>

772
00:51:14,790 --> 00:51:16,260
<font color="yellow">That's their demand.</font>

773
00:51:16,760 --> 00:51:18,260
<font color="yellow">It's out of my hands.</font>

774
00:51:18,660 --> 00:51:20,260
<font color="yellow">But from our perspective,</font>

775
00:51:20,590 --> 00:51:21,990
<font color="yellow">it's too large a risk.</font>

776
00:51:22,390 --> 00:51:23,730
<font color="yellow">Chairman Kang.</font>

777
00:51:23,730 --> 00:51:27,050
<font color="yellow">Even banks these days don't do refund guarantees.</font>

778
00:51:27,050 --> 00:51:28,190
<font color="yellow">That's your problem.</font>

779
00:51:28,690 --> 00:51:31,060
<font color="yellow">The shipowners won't sign unless it's a heavy tail payment.</font>

780
00:51:31,060 --> 00:51:32,090
<font color="yellow">It's up to you.</font>

781
00:51:32,690 --> 00:51:34,190
<font color="yellow">There are other shipbuilders.</font>

782
00:51:37,930 --> 00:51:40,230
<font color="yellow">We could help you with the finances.</font>

783
00:51:40,230 --> 00:51:41,960
<font color="yellow">Let us invest.</font>

784
00:51:43,160 --> 00:51:44,160
<font color="yellow">I don't want...</font>

785
00:51:44,560 --> 00:51:46,160
<font color="yellow">to borrow your money, too.</font>

786
00:51:46,590 --> 00:51:49,560
<font color="yellow">What should I tell the shipowners then?</font>

787
00:51:53,060 --> 00:51:55,660
<font color="yellow">Make up your mind. They're impatient people.</font>

788
00:51:57,560 --> 00:51:59,130
<font color="yellow">They can pay us later.</font>

789
00:51:59,790 --> 00:52:01,670
<font color="yellow">- Sir.
-  It's done, then.</font>

790
00:52:01,670 --> 00:52:02,690
<font color="yellow">I'll tell them that.</font>

791
00:52:05,060 --> 00:52:06,160
<font color="yellow">Is that it?</font>

792
00:52:09,230 --> 00:52:10,860
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan, wait for me.</font>

793
00:52:12,960 --> 00:52:15,090
<font color="yellow">Are you sure about this? It's too risky.</font>

794
00:52:22,560 --> 00:52:25,990
<font color="yellow">Mr Kim, set up a meeting with the bank presidents.</font>

795
00:52:30,390 --> 00:52:32,530
<font color="yellow">Stop Gun Woo from meeting people from the banks.</font>

796
00:52:33,390 --> 00:52:36,390
<font color="yellow">I doubt that will make him come to us for help.</font>

797
00:52:37,390 --> 00:52:38,690
<font color="yellow">Do Choong is back.</font>

798
00:52:39,190 --> 00:52:41,860
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo might ignore me, but he won't.</font>

799
00:52:42,260 --> 00:52:43,390
<font color="yellow">For Shin Young's sake.</font>

800
00:52:43,960 --> 00:52:45,030
<font color="yellow">I understand.</font>

801
00:52:46,030 --> 00:52:48,890
<font color="yellow">When will you release the MK2 vaccine?</font>

802
00:52:50,060 --> 00:52:51,760
<font color="yellow">First, I'll control their finances.</font>

803
00:52:52,260 --> 00:52:53,990
<font color="yellow">Then I'll go for Dodo Pharmaceutical.</font>

804
00:52:54,490 --> 00:52:56,090
<font color="yellow">If the holding company falls,</font>

805
00:52:56,490 --> 00:52:57,890
<font color="yellow">they will rot from the roots up.</font>

806
00:52:58,430 --> 00:53:00,590
<font color="yellow">Once it starts to rot, even a thousand-year-old tree...</font>

807
00:53:02,060 --> 00:53:04,130
<font color="yellow">will fall in an instant.</font>

808
00:53:11,230 --> 00:53:13,030
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan, Gun Woo.</font>

809
00:53:14,660 --> 00:53:18,240
<font color="yellow">They'll already be at loggerheads.</font>

810
00:53:18,240 --> 00:53:19,730
<font color="yellow">They just need some fanning.</font>

811
00:53:20,690 --> 00:53:22,330
<font color="yellow">When the fire rages,</font>

812
00:53:23,690 --> 00:53:26,490
<font color="yellow">one of them will go down in flames.</font>

813
00:53:36,930 --> 00:53:39,200
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you eating?</font>

814
00:53:39,200 --> 00:53:41,430
<font color="yellow">I'd rather eat sand.</font>

815
00:53:41,990 --> 00:53:43,660
<font color="yellow">I have no appetite.</font>

816
00:53:44,130 --> 00:53:46,760
<font color="yellow">Me, too.</font>

817
00:53:47,330 --> 00:53:48,390
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

818
00:53:49,330 --> 00:53:51,560
<font color="yellow">where will you stay tonight?</font>

819
00:53:52,930 --> 00:53:54,160
<font color="yellow">Let's go to Dodo Hotel.</font>

820
00:53:54,690 --> 00:53:56,960
<font color="yellow">We'll ask Shin Young to give us a suite.</font>

821
00:53:58,190 --> 00:53:59,330
<font color="yellow">Okay...</font>

822
00:54:08,030 --> 00:54:09,690
<font color="yellow">135 dollars, please.</font>

823
00:54:09,690 --> 00:54:12,490
<font color="yellow">Sure. I can afford that.</font>

824
00:54:12,490 --> 00:54:14,090
<font color="yellow">Here you go.</font>

825
00:54:19,260 --> 00:54:20,730
<font color="yellow">The card was suspended.</font>

826
00:54:21,930 --> 00:54:24,480
<font color="yellow">It can't be. It's a premium card.</font>

827
00:54:24,480 --> 00:54:26,530
<font color="yellow">This is unbelievable. Fine.</font>

828
00:54:26,960 --> 00:54:27,990
<font color="yellow">Try this one.</font>

829
00:54:33,990 --> 00:54:35,630
<font color="yellow">This is suspended, too.</font>

830
00:54:36,760 --> 00:54:37,960
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

831
00:54:41,030 --> 00:54:42,060
<font color="yellow">Try this one.</font>

832
00:54:46,260 --> 00:54:47,260
<font color="yellow">This, too.</font>

833
00:54:49,230 --> 00:54:51,160
<font color="yellow">Dad must've cut us off.</font>

834
00:54:53,490 --> 00:54:55,690
<font color="yellow">The old mule...</font>

835
00:54:56,160 --> 00:54:57,390
<font color="yellow">How dare he?</font>

836
00:54:59,430 --> 00:55:01,560
<font color="yellow">Calm down or you'll faint again.</font>

837
00:55:01,560 --> 00:55:02,860
<font color="yellow">Do Choong...</font>

838
00:55:10,060 --> 00:55:11,260
<font color="yellow">Il Jae asked me...</font>

839
00:55:11,990 --> 00:55:13,890
<font color="yellow">to give this to you.</font>

840
00:55:19,530 --> 00:55:21,330
<font color="yellow">(Do Gun Woo's slush fund)</font>

841
00:55:29,590 --> 00:55:32,260
<font color="yellow">Tax fraud, lobbying and illegal loans.</font>

842
00:55:33,230 --> 00:55:35,160
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo's management style...</font>

843
00:55:36,660 --> 00:55:39,660
<font color="yellow">is a lot like yours when you were younger.</font>

844
00:55:42,860 --> 00:55:45,190
<font color="yellow">Chimney sweeps get soot all over...</font>

845
00:55:46,130 --> 00:55:48,590
<font color="yellow">and fishmongers reek of fish.</font>

846
00:55:48,960 --> 00:55:50,390
<font color="yellow">A businessman...</font>

847
00:55:52,660 --> 00:55:55,010
<font color="yellow">is bound to touch dirty money.</font>

848
00:55:55,010 --> 00:55:56,830
<font color="yellow">That's what you think.</font>

849
00:55:58,230 --> 00:55:59,530
<font color="yellow">Did you...</font>

850
00:56:00,160 --> 00:56:02,180
<font color="yellow">rob Il Jae of B World?</font>

851
00:56:02,180 --> 00:56:03,190
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

852
00:56:05,430 --> 00:56:07,430
<font color="yellow">You said the process was sound.</font>

853
00:56:08,430 --> 00:56:10,860
<font color="yellow">When making a deal, both parties...</font>

854
00:56:10,860 --> 00:56:13,060
<font color="yellow">always think they got the worse end.</font>

855
00:56:13,390 --> 00:56:16,260
<font color="yellow">Buying it for half the market price is stealing.</font>

856
00:56:17,160 --> 00:56:18,660
<font color="yellow">What do you want?</font>

